# https://www.reddit.com/r/ChatGPT/comments/11twe7z/prompt_to_summarize/
SUMMARY_GENERATION_PROMPT_FROM_REDDIT = "Can you provide a comprehensive summary of the given text? The summary should cover all the key points and main ideas presented in the original text, while also condensing the information into a concise and easy-to-understand format. Please ensure that the summary includes relevant details and examples that support the main ideas, while avoiding any unnecessary information or repetition. The length of the summary should be appropriate for the length and complexity of the original text, providing a clear and accurate overview without omitting any important information."

# I gave the summary generation prompt from Reddit to ChatGPT and asked for a title generation version.
TITLE_GENERATION_PROMPT_BY_CHATGPT_BASED_ON_ONE_FROM_REDDIT = "Can you craft a succinct and engaging title for the given text? The title should encapsively capture the essence and main themes of the original text, reflecting its core message and significant points. Aim for a title that is both informative and intriguing, enticing readers to delve into the content. Ensure the title is appropriately tailored to the text's length and depth, summarizing its central ideas without revealing too much detail or straying from the text's main focus."

